Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
